snippet.title: Amber Heard and Elon Musk Rekindle Romance | Daily Celebrity News | Splash TV
snippet.description:
Amber Heard and Elon Musk were spotted going hand-in-hand on a sushi date in LA leading us to conclude that they are getting back together.

SUBSCRIBE NOW : https://goo.gl/JaLP0U

Sounds like Amber Heard has found a little love…

In an ex named Elon Musk.

You heard us right, the couple is apparently rekindling the romance as they were spotted hand in hand heading to a sushi date in LA.

And to make things even better, this all comes as it’s being revealed that Elon has agreed to a 10-year all-or-nothing deal worth an estimated $55 billion.

Yep.  Billion.  With a “B”.

The couple went their separate ways back in August of last year, and Musk admitted to Rolling Stone that he was hurt after the breakup…

And Amber revealed that she still cared for him.

Guess it’s nice to know this story has a happy ending.  That is if they stay together this time.
